label: public.home.content.subtitle
text: You're welcome to look around and start playing!

label: public.home.content.list.title
text: DeRivean is simple game, where you will:

label: public.home.content.list.item-0
text: Create your own heroes and take them to battle.

label: public.home.content.list.item-1
text: Gain experience in quite different way and build you kingdom.

label: public.home.content.list.item-2
text: Fight other players, pass stages and become most powerful king over here!

label: public.sign-up.content.title
text: Sign up to join World of DeRivean!

label: public.sign-up.content.subtitle
text: Just type a few things and start playing!

label: public.sign-up.content.list.title
text: This is a RPG game, where you will:

label: public.sign-up.content.list.item-1
text: Build up a Kingdom of Yours

label: public.sign-up.content.list.item-2
text: Gain resources, XP, level up Heroes, merge them

label: public.sign-up.content.list.item-3
text: Fight for becoming the greatest King over here

label: public.sign-up.content.list.item-4
text: ...and a lot more awaits for you!

label: public.sign-up.form.name.required
text: Please choose some name representing you!

label: public.sign-up.form.login.required
text: Please choose some login - for example your nick or email address.

label: public.sign-up.form.password.required
text: We still need everlasting passwords, so please pick some.

label: public.sign-in.content.subtitle
text: Login and look around, what's new!

label: public.sign-in.content.form.title
text: Open a magic gate by your password!

label: public.sign-in.form.login.required
text: We cannot make login request without... login!

label: public.sign-in.form.password.required
text: Please, give us your deepest secret!

label: public.sign-in.content.list.title
text: Check, what's new in your Kingdom

label: public.sign-in.content.list.item-0

label: public.sign-in.content.list.item-3
